item.title: Assemble For Training In 2023
item.description: This is an album of assemble for training in 2023. Start on 27/1/2023, and end on 31/1/2023. The training took place in Taipa Stadium and Lou Hau High School Macao. Except the third day (29/1/2023), took place in Lin Fong Sports Ground and Flora Garden. Last modified at 21:01 29/1/2023. First day (27/1/2023) The first day was surprisingly easy, not tired. The longest distance is 200m *4 and all 38s,
